data.description: This fantastic home has been lovingly maintained.  Situated in a quiet cul-de-sac in Nampa, this home is a must-see.  Walking into this home, you are greeted with vaulted ceilings, a large family room, and a cozy wood stove to warm you this winter.  The kitchen provides lots of open space, a new stove, a pantry, and a refrigerator.  The home has a split-bedroom layout as well. The backyard has a covered patio, a large shed with power, and plenty of room on the side to stack wood and space for RV Parking.  The 3-car garage has new epoxied floors, and the home comes fully equipped with full solar panels, a whole house water filtration system, and an air purifier on the HVAC system. No HOA in this neighborhood.  This home also has an assumable 2.75% mortgage for qualified buyers.  Ask listing agent for details.
